### Contact

### Experience
**Help Desk Technician** / Georgia Gwinnett College / January 2013 to Present    
**Responsibilities:**
* Updating the Support Services website.
* Created [web app](http://classroom.kyledornblaser.com) to track classroom availability.
* Troubleshoot and solve technology issues on campus.
* Find solutions to problems I have never seen before.

### Personal Project
**Game Loadouts** / [www.gameloadouts.com](http://www.gameloadouts.com) / [GitHub](https://github.com/Green-Squad/Tryhard-Loadouts)  
Game Loadouts is a PHP website built on the [Laravel](www.laravel.com) MVC framework. It is a community driven website for finding the best weapon loadouts in video games.  

### Skills
PHP, JavaScript, HTML, CSS, Java, SQL, Object Oriented Programming, Model-View-Controller Frameworks, Git, Photoshop, and Troubleshooting
